Quota is developed on:
  x86_64-redhat-linux-gnu     (RHEL 5)

Quota is tested on:
  x86_64-redhat-linux-gnu     (RHEL 5)
  powerpc64-unknown-linux-gnu (SLES 9)
  sparc-sun-solaris2.10       (Solaris 10 with gcc installed in /opt/sfw)
  sparc-sun-solaris2.11       (Solaris 11 with Sun C compiler)
  powerpc-ibm-aix5.2.0.0      (AIX 5.2 with gcc installed in /opt/freeware)
  powerpc-apple-darwin8.11.0

